headline: Could LyondellBasell’s 13% Weekly Surge Signal a Shift in Its 2025 Valuation?
summary: Wondering if LyondellBasell Industries is a bargain or overpriced? You are not alone. Plenty of investors are asking the same question right now. The stock recently shot up 13.2% in just the last week, though it is still down over 33% year-to-date, suggesting that sentiment and risk perception around the company have shifted rapidly.
